short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bookmark Cleaner is an extension that helps you keep your Chrome bookmark list simple.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bookmark Cleaner keeps your bookmarks neat by displaying and deleting bookmarks that have not been visited in the past year. Simplify your life.
long.ko: Bookmark Cleaner는 최근 1년간 한번도 방문하지 않은 북마크 목록을 보고 삭제할 수 있습니다. 삶을 단순화하세요.
